<%= form_tag worker_temporary_passwords_path %>
<p>Are you in the field, and need to invite dozens of volunteers? Click "Create Temporary Password," then shout it to your team. They may register themselves by clicking "<a href="/worker/temporary_passwords/new">I have a temporary password</a>" on the Login screen.</p>
<p>This password will expire 30 minutes from the time you create it. There is no limit to the number of passwords you may create.</p>
<div class="row">
	<div class="small-12 medium-5 large-4 columns invite">
	  <%= submit_tag "Generate Password", :onclick => "return confirm('Only share this temporary password with authorized, trusted people from your organization. Users who use this password will be connected with you.')", :class => "button" %>
	</div>   
</div>
<p class="temporary_password"><%= notice if notice and notice.include? "Temporary password" %></p>
</form>